name: Into the Unknown (itch) (fourtyTwoIsNotEnough)
description:
This game was created in 96 hours for the 2021 Community Jam (hosted by usenowgamer and Electric Glitch Studios).

Try to reach the, but you won't know what is the end until you get there.

Shooting with left click pointing at your cursor.
